00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:57,600
Good.

56
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:04,640
Hello, Mr. Chen.

57
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,280
Hello there, Mr. Chen.

58
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:10,520
Hello.

59
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:21,480
Mr. Chen.

60
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,640
Hello.

61
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,320
What a wonderful performance. It was brilliant.

62
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,380
Really excellent.

63
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,940
Young Marshal.

64
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:41,300
These audience members are something else.

65
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,920
Chen Zhiyi's performance of 'The Drunken Beauty'

66
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:44,000
is completely different

67
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,760
from the older generations.

68
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,440
Just look at everyone's reaction.

69
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,970
The changes are excellent.

70
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,450
Mr. Chen is impressive.

71
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:54,980
Young Marshal.

72
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:58,280
So regarding this time's top prize

73
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,600
and

74
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,500
the ownership of 'Old Dreams'

75
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,520
what do you think?

76
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:06,320
You've been here for so long now.

77
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,600
Our Fuchun Hall also...

78
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,480
