81
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,360
Given the chance,

82
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:19,000
I'd really like to meet this Mr. Chen again.

83
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:20,800
Let's go.

84
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:42,960
Suiqing.

85
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,080
This is the place.

86
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:46,560
It's here.

87
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,500
But where is everyone?

88
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,120
Zhiyi.

89
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,760
Here we come!

90
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:57,800
Long live Mule Society!

91
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:01,600
Now,

92
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,720
